<center><font size=7><b>Barbarian</b></font></center>
<center>Number of entries found: 6</center><p>
<center>
<table width=600>
<TR><TD bgcolor="blue" background=""><font color="white"><b><i>Tips</i></b></font></td></tr>
<TR><TD><b>(Palace)</b> Try and knock your opponent into a corner and kick him in the nether regions a
few times - then he'll soon bite the dust. When you reach Drax he'll throw a few
thunderbolts at you. Jump over the first one then roll into him. The Princess
sits at your feet and it's all over. Another tip is to get a friend to press
symbol shift or extended mode while you're fighting as this slows the whole
thing down giving you a reasonable chance to knock hell out of your opponent.
 <i>(YS Smash Tips)</i> 
<br>
</td></tr>
<TR><TD bgcolor="blue" background=""><font color="white"><b><i>Multiface pokes</i></b></font></td></tr>
